chess.domain.pieces

Class Rook

  • java.lang.Object
    • chess.domain.pieces.Piece
      • chess.domain.pieces.Rook

  • public class Rook
extends Piece
    This class corresponds physical rook-piece thus only containing knowledge of it's place and whether or not it has been moved so far. This class gives methods to access that data and also to clone this rook.
    Author:
    sami
